# Test Runner Module
#
# Modern test execution framework for Simple language.
# Supports multiple modes (interpreter, SMF, native), coverage tracking,
# and integration with the unified test/feature database.
#
# Public API:
#   - use app.test_runner_new.test_runner_main.{run_tests}
#   - use app.test_runner_new.test_db_migrate.{run_migration_cli, validate_databases}
#   - use app.test_runner_new.test_db_perf.{run_benchmarks}
#
# Internal Components:
#   - Test discovery and execution (test_runner_*)
#   - Database integration (test_db_*)
#   - Documentation generation (doc_generator, doctest_runner)
#   - Coverage tracking (test_runner_coverage)
#   - Rust test integration (rust_test_runner)
#   - SDoc test framework (sdoctest)

# All submodules are automatically available through the module system.
# The test runner is transitioning to use std.database.feature for
# unified test/feature tracking.

